色其大叫救人。和議既<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武手足請舉起右手</span>並接近首位舉手手足，比身邊既人馬上知道有幾多肯衝鋒既勇武係身邊。人數達至<span style=\"color: red;\">5:1狗以上衝鋒救人</span>，唔夠人請be water。<br />\n<br />\n舉手聚集係因為防止有和理非舉手錯判人數。<br />\n<br />\n如果此post得到認同請推置頂，並請大家準備兩色膠布。現場的支援手足請幫有裝同前線<br />\n既手足戴上。<br />\n<br />\n唔洗痴實架，重疊然後留反半條有痴力既就會變成手帶。<br />\n<br />\nRagnar.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴打 我highlight 左重點<br />\n推到上熱門啦 都幾有用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c7aef9e471593a6f8d0bc266dcf90d0767207a9","tid":1330341,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:09:13.000Z","msg":"見到有情報組post 會每條前線派一個通訊兵<br />\n加強溝通 前線手足見到留意下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔理你爭取咩先，你用暴力就一定錯？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1329924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1329924</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"96fe3dc23aaf345183435d4bf2902c57a08b238a","tid":1330341,"uid":119283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:09:46.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">721</span>"},{"pid":"7d352a18ff869a9f948821311168073801646200","tid":1330341,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:18:20.000Z","msg":"值得關注<br />\n<br />\n共識問題解決唔到<br />\n唔可以真正無大台"},{"pid":"c41055b1873212494f5e9e58f149b771b9b0baf0","tid":1330341,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:18:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f60ed8c696835585074480861731de9eb70377e5","tid":1330341,"uid":67223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:20:28.000Z","msg":"可行"},{"pid":"14ddb611ad6ee9b14caa380382adfecb6654d6bb","tid":1330341,"uid":180499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"