d":1330341,"uid":40448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:54:02.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"ded9e88b245b1e61f7f663cbd37eda7cb9096ea6","tid":1330341,"uid":1330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637c56dd89642d5bc8c7c507ad47bf5359efbbcd","tid":1330341,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:04:31.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>唔理衝唔衝 21去金鐘</strong></span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>唔理衝唔衝 21去金鐘</strong></span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>唔理衝唔衝 21去金鐘</strong></span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">一定要人 一定要幫 一定要去 各位努力！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Spread it!</div></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<code>1）有人講咗「唔好再覆」就唔好爭住屌一毛、恥笑一毛，亦唔好跟住留「唔好再覆」，否則等同推po。2）俾正負評前睇埋最後一頁，唔好俾第一頁帶風向。3）新聞po睇日期先覆，小心一毛伎倆：有人推舊po、出引戰po、傳聞po。最後，721去遊行！</code><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 七大訴求 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;\n一、徹底撤回修例\n二、收回暴動定義\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選\n六、要求永不落實「社會信用評分系統」\n七、要求移除全港「多功能智慧燈柱」</code></pre>"},{"pid":"2cfcdf36a4f6efec6a537fee260f4455bfcd7d0b","tid":1330341,"uid":150726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"076e44265ab4f94e40cf7052b92d54d9ef8c785e","tid":1330341,"uid":58103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:53:08.000Z","msg":"唔會個個有咩紅藍膠布 <br />\n而且唔係個個知紅藍代表咩<br />\n就咁 坐低 唔贊成 <br />\n企係到 贊成呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:04:56.000Z","msg":"呢啲 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xFyCA4z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxFyCA4z.png&h=2501eb50&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fac6b29e2d587b236a9e910d3604ae79831045ca","tid":1330341,"uid":249026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6305f521806e63ef5f5dc8ae92d262fe187ad2d1","tid":1330341,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:07:02.000Z","msg":"小隊互相照應得啦"},{"pid":"2b89515599b0ffda30911c85a76e5ccca808c65f","tid":1330341,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6481ed033d8bffd83c7dc7ba42448d26c875ffa7","tid":1330341,"uid":150726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T13:55:50.000Z","msg":"手足們：<br />\n<br />\n上水及沙田兩日前線極端混亂，行動完全無共識。<br />\n兼且有疑似藍營混入，不停放出謠言等。前線必須要馬上定立一套快速取得共識方法。<br />\n<br />\n一個大聲公<br />\n<br />\n每人左手藍膠布右手紅膠布。<br />\n<br />\n大聲公在該前線提出問題，前線舉紅贊成舉藍反對。<br />\n咁當然大部分問題唔可以用yes or no表決完，咁就請大聲公逐級問題表決。我相信守定退唔需要再傾一個鐘。<br />\n<br />\n多防線共識。請由各防線大聲公表決後代議。<br />\n<br />\n大聲公=通訊兵。請在大聲公上貼上標籤以區分自己身分。每次活動轉標籤（當然各防線是共同標籤）以防混水摸魚。<br />\n<br />\n膠布用途2<br />\n<br />\n我想問大家有無試過眼前手足比人夾走，而你又救唔到？<br />\n<br />\n我有，好幾次。但都有救到過人，但我認為唔夠。<br />\n<br />\n我建議，每次有人被夾走，勇武（因為和理非唔會衝，所以無表決權）可以舉起紅色其大叫救人。和議既勇武手足請舉起右手並接近首位舉手手足，比身邊既人馬上知道有幾多肯衝鋒既勇武係身邊。人數達至5:1狗以上衝鋒救人，唔夠人請be water。<br />\n<br />\n舉手聚集係因為防止有和理非舉手錯判人數。<br />\n<br />\n如果此post得到認同請推置頂，並請大家準備兩色膠布。現場的支援手足請幫有裝同前線<br />\n既手足戴上。<br />\n<br />\n唔洗痴實架，重疊然後留反半條有痴力既就會變成手帶。<br />\n<br />\nRagnar."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:09:11.000Z","msg":"哦 啫係之前講嘅手帶分組<br />\n目的係俾前線義士預計到<br />\n真係開戰時<br />\n會有幾多人真係留喺度作戰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但唔太建議</span><br />\n容易突顯咗義士嘅存在<br />\n唔夠be water<br />\n比如好易俾便衣跟"},{"pid":"25c496581f40c1eeacc643cf93f657c6db3d9405","tid":1330341,"uid":263221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:09:26.000Z","msg":"721 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a8f34f747354eb156baafecb8b6c26432c5638","tid":1330341,"uid":189652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:10:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a5c3eccb1723a42f49ef219af8386af0a1fda57","tid":1330341,"uid":99883,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:11:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">舉得手點得人數黎，手足已經畀人扑濕左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"da5c206d9f955d03e82a7feffdcc3b92f7f33073","tid":1330341,"uid":280547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:11:08.000Z","msg":"推，重要"},{"pid":"bf223f99000f8261698068ef1965c9fa9236c003","tid":1330341,"uid":269166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:15:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"592b175bfc49223001d4b9632f823da593c0538d","tid":1330341,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:15:31.000Z","msg":"電工膠布得唔得"},{"pid":"45e17628dbb8852ae9c18b49cd69d2c40ef101f7","tid":1330341,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:16:01.000Z","msg":"大家咪撚理720，無視就岩<br />\n無視720就係狠狠一巴車落去班藍絲廢老到<br />\n等佢地鳩行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全部聚焦721！！<br />\n幫推！！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［警告］720邊個去撐警就係鬼，比人打死都唔值得可憐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1329704\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1329704</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"664fa1171caae3276c1b47a58de144b2052ab541","tid":1330341,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:17:26.000Z","msg":"可以，但要推到多人知"},{"pid":"c8cf8c2d733c7a84e