islike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:59:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c5e5b654a500ee2c3b37f39051307830afaf01b","tid":1330341,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T10:00:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb124bcbeb473a6d398cbbc55b76d8ff4ff10fe6","tid":1330341,"uid":258377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T21:47:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">推哂d 有用嘅post 上嚟， 三毛死撚開DLLM<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n721 15:00 維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"78f3ad45f20fec45c1e9b4768b0321d9e725f884","tid":1330341,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T00:54:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f668228738a3ea5824f890adc235c9062cc76f72","tid":1330341,"uid":279357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6481ed033d8bffd83c7dc7ba42448d26c875ffa7","tid":1330341,"uid":150726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T13:55:50.000Z","msg":"手足們：<br />\n<br />\n上水及沙田兩日前線極端混亂，行動完全無共識。<br />\n兼且有疑似藍營混入，不停放出謠言等。前線必須要馬上定立一套快速取得共識方法。<br />\n<br />\n一個大聲公<br />\n<br />\n每人左手藍膠布右手紅膠布。<br />\n<br />\n大聲公在該前線提出問題，前線舉紅贊成舉藍反對。<br />\n咁當然大部分問題唔可以用yes or no表決完，咁就請大聲公逐級問題表決。我相信守定退唔需要再傾一個鐘。<br />\n<br />\n多防線共識。請由各防線大聲公表決後代議。<br />\n<br />\n大聲公=通訊兵。請在大聲公上貼上標籤以區分自己身分。每次活動轉標籤（當然各防線是共同標籤）以防混水摸魚。<br />\n<br />\n膠布用途2<br />\n<br />\n我想問大家有無試過眼前手足比人夾走，而你又救唔到？<br />\n<br />\n我有，好幾次。但都有救到過人，但我認為唔夠。<br />\n<br />\n我建議，每次有人被夾走，勇武（因為和理非唔會衝，所以無表決權）可以舉起紅色其大叫救人。和議既勇武手足請舉起右手並接近首位舉手手足，比身邊既人馬上知道有幾多肯衝鋒既勇武係身邊。人數達至5:1狗以上衝鋒救人，唔夠人請be water。<br />\n<br />\n舉手聚集係因為防止有和理非舉手錯判人數。<br />\n<br />\n如果此post得到認同請推置頂，並請大家準備兩色膠布。現場的支援手足請幫有裝同前線<br />\n既手足戴上。<br />\n<br />\n唔洗痴實架，重疊然後留反半條有痴力既就會變成手帶。<br />\n<br />\nRagnar."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:18:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">痞低起身做支持同反對會唔會明顯d<br />\n人多又遠係左定右係紅定藍好難睇清</span></span>"},{"pid":"2ae02b65b64abb2e9170bc5c76344697b1e82411","tid":1330341,"uid":137209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:18:39.000Z","msg":"721見"},{"pid":"3d0678c190684dee0097787c3261f1ea372561b0","tid":1330341,"uid":180657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:29:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d531587b661508193ff11ecdc027b0bf0850b593","tid":1330341,"uid":180657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T05:03:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5aa1e500b251aa8b8473976899081c3d71382001","tid":1330341,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T05:05:17.000Z","msg":"實用，推"},{"pid":"e198cda9ce11df3d566c2fd6fe443588f1963238","tid":1330341,"uid":180657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:11:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ca39317d926dc0e8847327853fa1ea1c93058d6","tid":1330341,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:14:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2a3e9e095ae1fc1ebf5348ceb33730f05f101406","tid":1330341,"uid":180657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:10:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81e07a1c10c2fd32272830d39e65a81c3d0cefa9","tid":1330341,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:11:42.000Z","msg":"救人都要投票，要人和議係咪on9<img sr